<title>USA: U.S. HEADLINE STOCKS - Issues to watch.</title>
<headline>U.S. HEADLINE STOCKS - Issues to watch.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-12-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Stocks to watch this morning:</p>
<p>* 3Com Corp said its fiscal second quarter profits from operations rose a better than expected 71 percent on strong sales of its computer networking gear. Shares were down 5/8 at 76-1/8 in after-hours trading Thursday.</p>
<p>* Boston Communications Group Inc said it expects a fourth quarter loss of $0.01-$0.02 a share and slower revenue and net income growth in the first half of 1997. Shares closed at eight.  </p>
<p>* Autodesk Inc and Softdesk Inc said Friday they had amended their definitive merger agreement, sweetening Autodesk's bid for Softdesk to $15 a share from $12.</p>
<p>Autodesk closed at 27-3/4 and Softdesk closed at 10-1/2.</p>
